{"tid":2103808,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"共產主義同法西斯主義應該勢不兩立，個何解中共反而咁似法西斯主義既？","createTime":"2020-07-11T12:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T19:09:18.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"873e380dcdc54e8d67486d30e32b1f12b68c1282","tid":2103808,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"法西斯主義（英語：Fascism；義大利語：Fascismo；德語：Faschismus；民國初年又譯作棒喝主義），字源為束棒（法西斯，一種古羅馬的象徵物），法西斯主義是一種激進的右翼，專制的極端民族主義形式，其特點是獨裁權力，強制鎮壓反對派，強大的社會和經濟地位，在20世紀初的歐洲起到了突出作用。 第一次法西斯運動在第一次世界大戰期間在義大利出現，然後傳播到其他歐洲國家。與自由主義，馬克思主義和無政府主義相反，法西斯主義被放置在傳統左右翼範圍內的極右翼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B3%95%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%AF%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25B9%2589&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyEy%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=47bb2520\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B3%95%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%AF%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89</a>"},{"pid":"ecfc4c92ed71b2381661f1e65d075eeefd5afabc","tid":2103808,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"法西斯係佢推共產嘅手段<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtJiMWw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtJiMWw.png&h=ebcf48b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0a9488c1221276511a4f1cbb7752840fd0696bc","tid":2103808,"uid":33848,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"支那邊忽共產主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc543af4494cac7307738e553b09c029a41a3b34","tid":2103808,"uid":34869,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:59:16.000Z","msg":"因為中共係披住共產皮既法西斯"},{"pid":"e02e390b7ec11a59c913913a2819f08731a670fc","tid":2103808,"uid":129812,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"因為中共唔係共產主義"},{"pid":